It's been a really long day.

54
00:07:22.652 --> 00:07:24.445
Can we get some rest?

55
00:07:26.781 --> 00:07:28.199
[STAIRCASE CREAKING]

56
00:07:29.283 --> 00:07:30.868
[PAUL AND SARAH CONTINUE, INDISTINCT]

57
00:07:52.181 --> 00:07:53.307
